<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.3">
<l>urutteḻu vāli mārvi lorukaṇai yuruva vōṭṭi</l>
<l>karuttuṭait tampik kiṉpak katirmuṭi yaraca ḷittāy</l>
<l>parutteḻu palavum māvum paḻamviḻun toḻukum nāṅkaik</l>
<l>karuttaṉē kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having discharged an arrow to penetrate into the chest of Vāli,</l>
<l rend="indent">who rose up in anger,</l>
<l>You who bestowed the crown that radiates joy and the kingdom</l>
<l rend="indent">to the younger brother who had an agreement [with you],</l>
<l>Creator, you in the cool hamlet of Kāvaḷam in Nāṅkai where fruits which fall</l>
<l>From high rising jack and mango [trees] ooze, only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
